Reviews.Title: Video balun
Reviews.Author: Joseph Olympio Marrazzo "Joe Marrzazzo"
Reviews.Content: works great screw hold downs for wire a little week if wire is of a small gauge but worked great for my project thanks

Reviews.Title: Great Product
Reviews.Author: Joshua M. Robinson "Purrfect Printing"
Reviews.Content: I was very happy to find this product. For years I have been looking at mismatched cctv cables and thought there must be a way to make things look professional and unified. I was searching amazon for cat 5e cable to put network jacks in every room of the house and came across these. I ordered 1000' of cat 5e cable and plan on using these to wire 8 cameras while wiring for the network. Everything will run to the home office so its centralized and best part is most of the wiring will be hidden.

Reviews.Title: Excellent
Reviews.Author: Jesus Cazares
Reviews.Content: It help me a lot in saving... It was the first time I buy them and it did the job...
